                                <p data-translate="0Hih1">
                                    Hermano’s In-house technicians provide the best reliable, and Complete range of home appliance
                                    repairing and installation services by using the appropriate verified materials and latest techniques.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <div class="column_attr clearfix mobile_align_center floatr">
                                <button type="button" class="action_button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" id="submit1" style="background-color:#275935;" data-translate="0bnw1">Book Now</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 reveal fade-left" style="padding:10% 30px">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <div class="column_attr clearfix mobile_align_center">
                                <h2 data-translate="0elec1">Electricity</h2>
                                <p data-translate="0oet1">
                                    Our Electrical team is well-trained with full knowledge of SOPs required for the work along with the
                                    latest equipment required for the Electric repair and fitting work for residential and commercial
                                    customers.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-12">
                            <div class="column_attr clearfix mobile_align_center floatr">
                                <button type="button" class="action_button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" id="submit2" style="background-color:#275935;" data-translate="0bnw1">Book Now</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
